The '''Aquilaris Grand Arena''' was a large arena in the capital [[Floating City]] on the beautiful ocean world [[Aquilaris]]. Thousands of spectators safely watched sports such as dangerous [[Podracing/Legends|podraces]] from the stands. Special guests hosted the races from repulsorlift viewing platforms. The [[Aquilaris Classic/Legends|Aquilaris Classic]], [[Sunken City/Legends|Sunken City]], and [[Bumpy's Breakers]] were all race courses that began at the arena.

